title: Bigfish Games-Supermarket Mania.Precraked
description:
It&#039;s Nikki`s first day of work at TORG Corp., a supermarket run by
robots. She`s a bit on edge. Step in and help her stock shelves to
the rafters to keep customers happy. Nikki must stay on her stylish
toes and clean spills promptly, otherwise the rival superstore will
shut your store down. Enjoy 50 manic, yet fun-filled levels in
Supermarket Mania, everyones favorite one-stop shop.

CPU: 800 Mhz
RAM: 128 MB
